      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform. The 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 remains mechanically flawless, delivering linear power through eight individual throttle bodies up to the 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen features a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a fully functional Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system for precise suspension articulation. The chassis is impeccably preserved with zero oxidation, and the variable M-differential lock operates within factory tolerances. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the long-term integrity of the rotating assembly. With original factory paint and a pristine undercarriage, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
